authd (0.2.1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Adjust Rust dependencies
    - Rollback cc to 1.83: Version 1.84 was removed due to some problems with
      other ecosystems.
    - Bump transitive dependencies to latest SemVer version to fix
      RUSTSEC-2024-0003
